    <h2>Page List</h2>

    <div class="page_list">
      <p><a href = /home class='page_label'>Home Page</a></p>
      <p class='page_description'>This page shows options to Log-In, Create Account, or Browse the database.</p>

      <p><a href = /login class='page_label'>User Login</a></p>
      <p class='page_description'>This page prompts the user for their  blacksmith username/password and has options to go back to the Home Page or Create an Account.</p>

      <p><a href = /newuser class='page_label'>Create Account</a></p>
      <p class='page_description'> This page effectively “inserts” a blacksmith into the database by allowing them to create a blacksmith account.</p>

      <p><a href = /browse class='page_label'>Browse Page</a></p>
      <p class='page_description'>If not logged in, this page gives the user options to search Weapons, Enchantments, Materials, or Blacksmiths. <br><br> If logged in, this page gives the user options to search Weapons, Enchantments, Materials, or Blacksmiths as well as giving them the option to view their own Profile.</p>

      <p><a href = /browseWeapons class='page_label'>Search Weapons Page</a></p>
      <p class='page_description'>Here, the user can search for certain weapons by their names.</p>

      <p><a href = /browseMaterials class='page_label'>Search Materials Page</a></p>
      <p class='page_description'>Here, the user can search for certain materials by their names.</p>

      <p><a href = /browseEnchantments class='page_label'>Search Enchantments Page</a></p>
      <p class='page_description'>Here, the user can search for certain enchantments by their names.</p>

      <p><a href = /browseBlacksmiths class='page_label'>Search Blacksmiths Page</a></p>
      <p class='page_description'>Here, the user can search for certain blacksmiths by their names.</p>

      <p><a href = /profile class='page_label'>User Profile Page</a></p>
      <p class='page_description'>This page lists weapons made (can link to specific weapon page), materials owned (can link to specific material page), location, and current/past mentors/mentees the blacksmith has had.</p>

      <p><a href = /editprofile class='page_label'>Profile Editor</a></p>
      <p class='page_description'>This page allows logged-in blacksmiths to add new mentor/mentee training relationships, add/remove weapons, add/remove owned materials, and/or change their experience level.</p>

      <p><a href = /weapon class='page_label'>Weapons Page</a></p>
      <p class='page_description'>This page shows the stats, materials, and enchantments of each weapon.</p>

      <p><a href = /material class='page_label'>Materials Page</a></p>
      <p class='page_description'>This page shows the stats, current weapons, and current enchantments that use each material.</p>

      <p><a href = /enchant class='page_label'>Enchantments Page</a></p>
      <p class='page_description'>This page shows stats, experience requirement, material requirements, and current weapons with each enchantment.</p>
